{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-changelog-js","path":"/changelog/2016/june","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"hacktivity-upvoting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hacktivity-upvoting\" aria-label=\"hacktivity upvoting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hacktivity Upvoting</h3>\n<p>Users can now upvote reports that they’re interested in in order to create a “Popular” sorting on Hacktivity where reports with the most upvotes are featured on top.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"june_2016_upvoting\"\n        title=\"june_2016_upvoting\"\n        src=\"/static/71a1ca87401d668d6d07a6b4925bccaa/0b533/june_2016_upvoting.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/71a1ca87401d668d6d07a6b4925bccaa/fac75/june_2016_upvoting.png 125w,\n/static/71a1ca87401d668d6d07a6b4925bccaa/63868/june_2016_upvoting.png 250w,\n/static/71a1ca87401d668d6d07a6b4925bccaa/0b533/june_2016_upvoting.png 500w,\n/static/71a1ca87401d668d6d07a6b4925bccaa/9be90/june_2016_upvoting.png 636w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"hacker-leaderboard\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hacker-leaderboard\" aria-label=\"hacker leaderboard permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hacker Leaderboard</h3>\n<p>We’ve deprecated the Thanks page at <a href=\"https://hackerone.com/thanks\">https://hackerone.com/thanks</a> and turned it into a hacker leaderboard that’s segmented into more granular time periods and sortable by Signal, Impact, and Reputation. See who’s on top <a href=\"https://hackerone.com/leaderboard\">here</a>.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"june_2016_leaderboard\"\n        title=\"june_2016_leaderboard\"\n        src=\"/static/c1d3e273e486449a07f18fafd1886d48/0b533/june_2016_leaderboard.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c1d3e273e486449a07f18fafd1886d48/fac75/june_2016_leaderboard.png 125w,\n/static/c1d3e273e486449a07f18fafd1886d48/63868/june_2016_leaderboard.png 250w,\n/static/c1d3e273e486449a07f18fafd1886d48/0b533/june_2016_leaderboard.png 500w,\n/static/c1d3e273e486449a07f18fafd1886d48/1d69c/june_2016_leaderboard.png 750w,\n/static/c1d3e273e486449a07f18fafd1886d48/00d43/june_2016_leaderboard.png 1000w,\n/static/c1d3e273e486449a07f18fafd1886d48/e4ba2/june_2016_leaderboard.png 1468w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"badges\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#badges\" aria-label=\"badges permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Badges</h3>\n<p>Hackers can now receive badges when they meet certain criteria or achieve certain events to showcase on their profile.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.400000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"june_2016_badges\"\n        title=\"june_2016_badges\"\n        src=\"/static/aa5c61bed25a37508cebe52f41c356b0/0b533/june_2016_badges.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa5c61bed25a37508cebe52f41c356b0/fac75/june_2016_badges.png 125w,\n/static/aa5c61bed25a37508cebe52f41c356b0/63868/june_2016_badges.png 250w,\n/static/aa5c61bed25a37508cebe52f41c356b0/0b533/june_2016_badges.png 500w,\n/static/aa5c61bed25a37508cebe52f41c356b0/1d69c/june_2016_badges.png 750w,\n/static/aa5c61bed25a37508cebe52f41c356b0/5caea/june_2016_badges.png 996w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"api-documentation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#api-documentation\" aria-label=\"api documentation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>API Documentation</h3>\n<p>We introduce the first version of the HackerOne API to empower programs to build custom metrics and dashboards. Learn more about our <a href=\"https://www.hackerone.com/blog/launching-the-hackerone-api\">API Documentation</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"ui-improvements-to-default-automatic-invitations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ui-improvements-to-default-automatic-invitations\" aria-label=\"ui improvements to default automatic invitations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UI Improvements to Default Automatic Invitations</h3>\n<p>We’ve cleaned up the UI to Invite Hackers so that it’s clear that there’s a single call-to-action to privately launch a program by turning automatic invitations on.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 20%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"june_2016_automatic_invites\"\n        title=\"june_2016_automatic_invites\"\n        src=\"/static/a96d476d7ee1a302ef0c251cb17bea81/0b533/june_2016_automatic_invites.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a96d476d7ee1a302ef0c251cb17bea81/fac75/june_2016_automatic_invites.png 125w,\n/static/a96d476d7ee1a302ef0c251cb17bea81/63868/june_2016_automatic_invites.png 250w,\n/static/a96d476d7ee1a302ef0c251cb17bea81/0b533/june_2016_automatic_invites.png 500w,\n/static/a96d476d7ee1a302ef0c251cb17bea81/1d69c/june_2016_automatic_invites.png 750w,\n/static/a96d476d7ee1a302ef0c251cb17bea81/00d43/june_2016_automatic_invites.png 1000w,\n/static/a96d476d7ee1a302ef0c251cb17bea81/7a1fb/june_2016_automatic_invites.png 1030w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>  </p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/changelog/2016/june","title":"June 2016"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}